Can't attach a tarball, so here you go:
1. Create a `Dockerfile` with the following contents:
```Dockerfile
FROM docker.io/ubuntu
```
2. Create a context tarball: `tar -cvf context.tar Dockerfile`
3. Call Remote API: `varlink call unix:///run/podman/io.podman/io.podman.BuildImage '{"build":{"contextDir":"/path/to/context.tar","dockerfiles":["Dockerfile"]}}' -m`
